    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Don't reopen files in Sublime Text 2]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.benjaminguillet.com/blog/2013/07/11/dont-reopen-files-in-sublime-text-2/"/>
    <updated>2013-07-11T00:40:00-07:00</updated>
    <id>http://www.benjaminguillet.com/blog/2013/07/11/dont-reopen-files-in-sublime-text-2</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Just add this to your settings:</p>

<p><code>
"hot_exit": false,
"remember_open_files": false # ignored if hot_exit is true.
</code></p>
